) proximal to tarsala, subterminala (
ζ
), parasubterminala (
z
), pretarsala (
ζ
). Leg II: coxa 1B; trochanter 1B; basifemur 2B; telofemur 4B; genu 3B, genuala; tibia 6B, 2 tibialae (
φ
); tarsus 16B, tarsala (
ω
), microtarsala (
ε
) not observed, pretarsala (
ζ
). Leg III: coxa 1B; trochanter 1B; basifemur 2B; telofemur 3B; genu 3B, genuala; tibia 6B, tibiala; tarsus 15B.

